  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We, the researchers at Lawson Health Research Institute, propose to investigate the impact
      of surgical ischemia and reperfusion on skeletal muscle microcirculation using a hand-held
      microscope.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We propose to investigate the impact of surgical ischemia and reperfusion on skeletal muscle
      microcirculation using a hand-held microscope.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
